00:25:17,307 --> 00:25:18,237
Your relatives,

579
00:25:18,947 --> 00:25:19,876
friends,

580
00:25:20,346 --> 00:25:21,396
or coursemates,

581
00:25:22,227 --> 00:25:24,396
is there really no one you can contact?

582
00:25:25,106 --> 00:25:26,037
Buddy,

583
00:25:26,826 --> 00:25:29,037
how did you slip so far?

584
00:25:51,426 --> 00:25:52,105
Xiang Nan.

585
00:25:52,106 --> 00:25:52,786
You're back.

586
00:25:52,787 --> 00:25:53,676
Are you going out?

587
00:25:53,866 --> 00:25:55,396
I'm heading to my studio.

588
00:25:58,866 --> 00:25:59,865
Did my brother

589
00:25:59,866 --> 00:26:01,277
take you to his construction site
two days ago?

590
00:26:01,866 --> 00:26:03,156
Yes. Why?

591
00:26:06,507 --> 00:26:07,625
Your construction was suspended

592
00:26:07,626 --> 00:26:08,665
because of the procedural issues.

593
00:26:08,666 --> 00:26:10,356
It has nothing to do with me, right?

594
00:26:14,027 --> 00:26:16,277
Did you investigate this?
Was that really necessary?

595
00:26:16,666 --> 00:26:18,517
I didn't investigate it.
Someone told me.

596
00:26:19,987 --> 00:26:21,026
Who told you?

597
00:26:21,027 --> 00:26:22,317
Does it even matter?

598
00:26:22,707 --> 00:26:24,997
What matters is, why you lied to me?

599
00:26:25,227 --> 00:26:27,277
You condemned me
for something I didn't do.

600
00:26:28,186 --> 00:26:29,916
Don't make it sound so serious.

601
00:26:30,386 --> 00:26:32,836
I'm under tremendous stress
because of you.

602
00:26:35,146 --> 00:26:36,356
Weren't the results good anyway?

603
00:26:37,386 --> 00:26:38,865
Otherwise, you wouldn't have

604
00:26:38,866 --> 00:26:40,237
apologized to Biao.

605
00:26:42,866 --> 00:26:44,266
Why do I have to apologize?

606
00:26:44,267 --> 00:26:45,706
Is that really important?

607
00:26:45,707 --> 00:26:46,957
Yes, it's very important.

608
00:26:47,586 --> 00:26:48,836
If you had just listened to me

609
00:26:49,067 --> 00:26:50,636
and apologized to Biao,

610
00:26:51,227 --> 00:26:53,237
I wouldn't have done that to you.

611
00:26:54,787 --> 00:26:56,436
So you're admitting it?

612
00:26:58,507 --> 00:27:01,076
Did you really
have to pull such tricks on me?

613
00:27:02,826 --> 00:27:03,717
I did it

614
00:27:04,067 --> 00:27:05,076
to keep us out of harm's way

615
00:27:05,467 --> 00:27:06,436
and for efficiency.

616
00:27:06,787 --> 00:27:07,676
Also,

617
00:27:08,307 --> 00:27:09,836
stay out of my work

618
00:27:10,067 --> 00:27:11,436
from now on.

619
00:27:12,146 --> 00:27:13,596
I don't like it.

620
00:27:16,186 --> 00:27:18,197
I don't like it either.

621
00:27:25,067 --> 00:27:25,997
Come in.

622
00:27:28,106 --> 00:27:28,706
Mr. Jiang,

623
00:27:28,707 --> 00:27:29,466
Mr. Tao from the engineering division

624
00:27:29,467 --> 00:27:30,557
is waiting outside.

625
00:27:30,707 --> 00:27:31,757
Show him in.

626
00:27:31,947 --> 00:27:32,876
All right.

627
00:27:55,467 --> 00:27:56,396
Zhong.

628
00:27:56,707 --> 00:27:58,076
Why did you come here?

629
00:27:58,826 --> 00:27:59,997
Well,

630
00:28:00,626 --> 00:28:04,317
I got the certificate
as a smell specialist.

631
00:28:04,747 --> 00:28:05,825
Really?

632
00:28:05,826 --> 00:28:07,356
Congrats!

633
00:28:07,626 --> 00:28:08,596
Besides,

634
00:28:08,747 --> 00:28:09,986
there were more than 8,000 participants

635
00:28:09,987 --> 00:28:11,066
from the Ministry
of Ecology and Environment

636
00:28:11,067 --> 00:28:12,116
in the training.

637
00:28:12,346 --> 00:28:14,517
Only 36 passed the exam.

638
00:28:15,626 --> 00:28:16,625
What a surprise!

639
00:28:16,626 --> 00:28:18,596
You're at the top of the heap.

640
00:28:19,307 --> 00:28:20,905
So I thought

641
00:28:20,906 --> 00:28:22,317
maybe we could

642
00:28:22,666 --> 00:28:25,116
celebrate today.

643
00:28:25,186 --> 00:28:26,665
Sure. Of course, we must celebrate this.

644
00:28:26,666 --> 00:28:27,306
I'll buy you a meal.

645
00:28:27,307 --> 00:28:28,477
Anything you like.

646
00:28:29,346 --> 00:28:31,105
I also wanted to thank you

647
00:28:31,106 --> 00:28:32,517
for helping me with my driving practice.

648
00:28:34,186 --> 00:28:35,317
Well,

649
00:28:36,666 --> 00:28:37,636
let's go to our usual place.

650
00:28:38,947 --> 00:28:40,317
Are you trying to save me some money?

651
00:28:41,507 --> 00:28:42,066
Let's go.

652
00:28:42,067 --> 00:28:42,836
Sure.

653
00:28:43,507 --> 00:28:45,676
Well done. I really didn't expect that.

654
00:28:47,027 --> 00:28:49,676
So your training session has ended?

655
00:28:50,186 --> 00:28:51,197
Yes.

656
00:28:53,307 --> 00:28:54,557
Are you

657
00:28:55,146 --> 00:28:56,957
going back to your unit?

658
00:28:59,547 --> 00:29:00,836
Yes, right.

659
00:29:04,787 --> 00:29:09,436
I guess we won't run into each other

660
00:29:09,906 --> 00:29:11,797
on the subway anymore.

661
00:29:12,146 --> 00:29:13,145
That's good for you.

662
00:29:13,146 --> 00:29:14,596
I hate squeezing in on the subway.

663
00:29:19,346 --> 00:29:20,317
Zhong,

664
00:29:20,626 --> 00:29:23,116
do you really plan to work

665
00:29:23,586 --> 00:29:25,266
in Shanghai in the long term?

666
00:29:25,267 --> 00:29:25,746
Yes.

667
00:29:25,747 --> 00:29:27,546
I enjoy my current job.

668
00:29:27,547 --> 00:29:28,185
You know what?

669
00:29:28,186 --> 00:29:31,596
Two of my articles
got over ten million views.

670
00:29:32,227 --> 00:29:33,037
I know.

671
00:29:33,106 --> 00:29:33,706
You do?

672
00:29:33,707 --> 00:29:34,345
Right.

673
00:29:34,346 --> 00:29:35,625
I subscribed to your public account.

674
00:29:35,626 --> 00:29:39,037
I've read all your articles.

675
00:29:39,106 --> 00:29:40,237
You read them all?

676
00:29:40,267 --> 00:29:41,266
What do you think?

677
00:29:41,267 --> 00:29:43,037
Incredible.

678
00:29:43,106 --> 00:29:44,625
Don't exaggerate.

679
00:29:44,626 --> 00:29:45,226
I'm not.

680
00:29:45,227 --> 00:29:45,665
I mean it.

681
00:29:45,666 --> 00:29:46,876
They are incredible.

682
00:29:48,307 --> 00:29:50,066
You know what? One of my readers

683
00:29:50,067 --> 00:29:51,706
sent me a private message.

684
00:29:51,707 --> 00:29:53,466
I was quite touched.

685
00:29:53,467 --> 00:29:54,596
He said

686
00:29:54,707 --> 00:29:57,676
he read two of my articles
about commuting,

687
00:29:57,866 --> 00:29:58,786
and they gave him a lump in his throat.

688
00:29:58,787 --> 00:30:01,066
He's tired from the daily commuting,

689
00:30:01,067 --> 00:30:02,385
but he still perseveres

690
00:30:02,386 --> 00:30:04,596
with the job he likes.

691
00:30:05,106 --> 00:30:06,836
He felt encouraged.

692
00:30:07,227 --> 00:30:08,145
That made me realize

693
00:30:08,146 --> 00:30:12,396
that my current job was meaningful.

694
00:30:14,227 --> 00:30:15,596
Yes, it's incredibly meaningful.

695
00:30:16,067 --> 00:30:17,105
Can you say something

696
00:30:17,106 --> 00:30:18,596
other than "incredible"?

697
00:30:19,027 --> 00:30:20,517
Well, I just...

698
00:30:20,747 --> 00:30:21,946
I just want to say

699
00:30:21,947 --> 00:30:24,266
it's incredible.

700
00:30:24,267 --> 00:30:25,557
Well, enough with the compliments.

701
00:30:28,707 --> 00:30:30,436
You need to keep up
the good work as well.

702
00:30:31,787 --> 00:30:32,557
Sure.

703
00:30:33,467 --> 00:30:34,436
I will.

704
00:30:42,787 --> 00:30:44,466
Ma'am, I'd like a bowl of prawn noodles.

705
00:30:44,467 --> 00:30:45,105
What about you?

706
00:30:45,106 --> 00:30:45,905
Eel noodles.

707
00:30:45,906 --> 00:30:46,706
A bowl of eel noodles.

708
00:30:46,707 --> 00:30:47,665
Order some more.

709
00:30:47,666 --> 00:30:49,546
Do you want some gravy?

710
00:30:49,547 --> 00:30:50,385
I can't eat much.

711
00:30:50,386 --> 00:30:50,825
No?

712
00:30:50,826 --> 00:30:52,356
It's on me. Eat as much as you like.

713
00:30:52,866 --> 00:30:53,746
Are you sure that's enough?

714
00:30:53,747 --> 00:30:54,786
All right, that's it.

715
00:30:54,787 --> 00:30:55,517
Okay.

716
00:30:55,547 --> 00:30:56,557
Thank you.

717
00:30:56,787 --> 00:30:58,425
Pick your orders up over there.

718
00:30:58,426 --> 00:31:00,237
Who wants fish bone broth noodles?

719
00:31:00,267 --> 00:31:02,105
No, I don't want.

720
00:31:02,106 --> 00:31:03,277
You don't want this, either?

721
00:31:03,386 --> 00:31:04,546
- What is that?
- Don't look back.

722
00:31:04,547 --> 00:31:05,546
My old man is over there.

723
00:31:05,547 --> 00:31:06,345
Don't eat it if you don't want to.

724
00:31:06,346 --> 00:31:06,706
I want.

725
00:31:06,707 --> 00:31:07,477
Let's go.

726
00:31:07,507 --> 00:31:08,636
Fine, I'll eat it myself.

727
00:31:09,227 --> 00:31:10,676
- Look at them.
- It's delicious.

728
00:31:17,067 --> 00:31:18,076
Xiang Zhong.

729
00:31:26,267 --> 00:31:26,905
Dad,

730
00:31:26,906 --> 00:31:27,916
you're here?

731
00:31:28,386 --> 00:31:29,436
Haiyang,

732
00:31:30,507 --> 00:31:33,717
are you eating here together?

733
00:31:34,787 --> 00:31:37,436
We just happened to run into each other.

734
00:31:37,547 --> 00:31:38,266
Right.

735
00:31:38,267 --> 00:31:41,277
We ran into each other.

736
00:31:43,186 --> 00:31:45,116
What's so special about today?

737
00:31:45,267 --> 00:31:47,517
Why does everyone eat noodles today?

738
00:31:48,267 --> 00:31:49,237
Come on in.

739
00:31:49,346 --> 00:31:50,546
No. You go ahead.

740
00:31:50,547 --> 00:31:51,345
Well.

741
00:31:51,346 --> 00:31:53,546
Mom and the kids are waiting
for you inside.

742
00:31:53,547 --> 00:31:54,636
We're leaving, then.

743
00:31:54,666 --> 00:31:55,596
Okay.

744
00:31:56,386 --> 00:31:57,237
Xiang Zhong,

745
00:31:57,747 --> 00:32:00,517
how did you know the kids were inside?

746
00:32:00,866 --> 00:32:02,076
Did you see us?

747
00:32:02,426 --> 00:32:04,625
Qian sent them to Kunshan,

748
00:32:04,626 --> 00:32:07,197
so I guess you wouldn't be here
without them, right?

749
00:32:08,106 --> 00:32:08,957
Exactly.

750
00:32:09,027 --> 00:32:10,636
Let's go inside.

751
00:32:10,666 --> 00:32:11,957
Something came up. I have to go now.

752
00:32:12,067 --> 00:32:13,757
Let's go, Haiyang.

753
00:32:14,707 --> 00:32:15,717
Are you hungry?

754
00:32:16,666 --> 00:32:17,746
I...

755
00:32:17,747 --> 00:32:18,596
I...

756
00:32:19,307 --> 00:32:20,277
Are you hungry?

757
00:32:21,186 --> 00:32:22,266
I... I want noodles.

758
00:32:22,267 --> 00:32:23,356
That's right. Come with me.

759
00:32:23,426 --> 00:32:24,596
But I'm not hungry.

760
00:32:25,067 --> 00:32:27,105
Oh, dear. What now?

761
00:32:27,106 --> 00:32:29,156
I got to go now.

762
00:32:29,186 --> 00:32:29,905
I should get going, too.

763
00:32:29,906 --> 00:32:30,997
All right.

764
00:32:32,067 --> 00:32:34,026
I need to work overtime.

765
00:32:34,027 --> 00:32:35,237
I'm going that way.

766
00:32:35,307 --> 00:32:36,197
Okay.

767
00:32:36,586 --> 00:32:37,145
Bye-bye.

768
00:32:37,146 --> 00:32:37,706
Sure.

769
00:32:37,707 --> 00:32:38,797
Bye, Dad.

770
00:32:53,346 --> 00:32:54,356
You're back, Madam.

771
00:32:57,826 --> 00:32:58,636
What is it?

772
00:32:59,027 --> 00:33:01,557
Mr. Jiang locked Xiaotong in the gym room

773
00:33:01,626 --> 00:33:03,156
and took her phone.

774
00:33:03,507 --> 00:33:05,997
Xiaotong was yelling just now.

775
00:33:06,386 --> 00:33:07,477
Why?

776
00:33:20,866 --> 00:33:21,876
Xiaotong.

777
00:33:25,067 --> 00:33:25,997
Xiang Nan,

778
00:33:27,267 --> 00:33:28,145
is that you?

779
00:33:28,146 --> 00:33:29,145
Yes, it's me.

780
00:33:29,146 --> 00:33:30,876
Can you let me out?

781
00:33:31,987 --> 00:33:33,105
Why did your dad

782
00:33:33,106 --> 00:33:34,356
lock you up?

783
00:33:34,787 --> 00:33:36,066
I need to see Guy.

784
00:33:36,067 --> 00:33:37,625
I must see him.

785
00:33:37,626 --> 00:33:39,156
He's leaving today.

786
00:33:39,866 --> 00:33:41,757
I just want to say goodbye.

787
00:33:42,787 --> 00:33:44,916
It's no use telling me this.

788
00:33:45,346 --> 00:33:46,836
You should talk to your dad.

789
00:33:47,426 --> 00:33:48,546
If it weren't for Jiang Hongbin,

790
00:33:48,547 --> 00:33:49,876
he wouldn't have left.

791
00:33:50,826 --> 00:33:52,345
Jiang Hongbin kept
pressuring Guy's family

792
00:33:52,346 --> 00:33:53,865
through the school,

793
00:33:53,866 --> 00:33:55,665
forcing him to transfer.

794
00:33:55,666 --> 00:33:57,797
His mother is taking him to Guangxi.

795
00:33:58,747 --> 00:34:00,557
If I don't see him today,

796
00:34:00,586 --> 00:34:02,557
I won't be able to meet him again.

797
00:34:09,146 --> 00:34:11,076
Are you still there, Xiang Nan?

798
00:34:13,786 --> 00:34:14,757
Yes, I am.

799
00:34:27,266 --> 00:34:28,677
Madam, Xiantong, you are back.

800
00:34:31,666 --> 00:34:32,677
Madam,

801
00:34:32,867 --> 00:34:34,426
Mr. Jiang

802
00:34:34,427 --> 00:34:35,597
came home early without notice.

803
00:34:35,626 --> 00:34:37,637
He asks you to go to his study.

804
00:34:41,507 --> 00:34:42,317
All right.

805
00:34:42,507 --> 00:34:43,516
Got it.

806
00:34:45,306 --> 00:34:46,356
Don't worry.

807
00:34:46,387 --> 00:34:47,516
Go upstairs first.

808
00:34:47,867 --> 00:34:49,317
I'll talk to him.

809
00:34:50,226 --> 00:34:51,597
It'll be all right. Don't worry.

810
00:35:06,427 --> 00:35:08,197
Why are you back so early?

811
00:35:10,266 --> 00:35:11,426
Would you rather

812
00:35:11,427 --> 00:35:12,597
I come back late?

813
00:35:15,387 --> 00:35:16,277
Yes.

814
00:35:16,786 --> 00:35:17,426
Then,

815
00:35:17,427 --> 00:35:19,036
I wouldn't have to explain anything.

816
00:35:27,467 --> 00:35:28,466
If I hadn't found out

817
00:35:28,467 --> 00:35:29,757
Jiang Xiaotong was gone,

818
00:35:30,586 --> 00:35:32,197
were you not going to tell me?

819
00:35:34,146 --> 00:35:35,836
As if you need me to tell you.

820
00:35:35,947 --> 00:35:36,986
You have so many spies

821
00:35:36,987 --> 00:35:38,717
keeping an eye on us.

822
00:35:39,306 --> 00:35:40,797
There's nothing we can hide from you.

823
00:35:44,827 --> 00:35:46,157
Where did you go earlier?

824
00:35:48,626 --> 00:35:49,956
We went to say goodbye to Guy.

825
00:35:50,827 --> 00:35:51,996
Who is Guy?

826
00:35:53,947 --> 00:35:56,717
He's the boy
whom you forced to transfer.

827
00:36:01,586 --> 00:36:02,476
Xiang Nan,

828
00:36:03,706 --> 00:36:04,797
do you know

829
00:36:05,507 --> 00:36:08,117
why I locked Xiaotong in the room?

830
00:36:08,547 --> 00:36:10,225
You know very well

831
00:36:10,226 --> 00:36:12,036
I want to keep her away from that thug.

832
00:36:13,306 --> 00:36:15,197
Why did you take her to see him?

833
00:36:15,266 --> 00:36:16,996
Did you do it on purpose?

834
00:36:19,706 --> 00:36:20,826
Did you have no friends

835
00:36:20,827 --> 00:36:21,996
when you were a teenager?

836
00:36:23,786 --> 00:36:26,026
Their teenage friendship is precious.

837
00:36:26,027 --> 00:36:27,956
Besides, the boy is leaving today.

838
00:36:28,467 --> 00:36:29,866
Can't you let Xiaotong

839
00:36:29,867 --> 00:36:30,757
keep a good memory with him?

840
00:36:32,507 --> 00:36:33,637
Friendship?

841
00:36:36,186 --> 00:36:37,305
Do you know what her relationship

842
00:36:37,306 --> 00:36:38,436
with that brat is?

843
00:36:39,467 --> 00:36:40,705
I believe in what she said.

844
00:36:40,706 --> 00:36:41,836
I do not.

845
00:36:42,106 --> 00:36:42,986
When she told me

846
00:36:42,987 --> 00:36:44,516
she was bullied at school,

847
00:36:44,827 --> 00:36:45,836
do you know

848
00:36:47,106 --> 00:36:48,105
how many sleepless nights

849
00:36:48,106 --> 00:36:48,996
I had over that?

850
00:36:49,347 --> 00:36:51,757
If I had insisted
on keeping her back then,

851
00:36:52,306 --> 00:36:54,157
she wouldn't have been hurt.

852
00:36:54,507 --> 00:36:56,197
I even thought of going to Canada myself

853
00:36:57,067 --> 00:36:59,876
to teach those thugs a lesson.

854
00:37:03,387 --> 00:37:06,386
But all my worries seem
to be a joke to her.

855
00:37:06,387 --> 00:37:07,906
What if she's telling the truth this time?

856
00:37:07,907 --> 00:37:09,105
What if she didn't lie to you?

857
00:37:09,106 --> 00:37:10,836
I don't care whether it's true or not.

858
00:37:13,106 --> 00:37:13,996
Xiang Nan,

859
00:37:14,467 --> 00:37:16,277
I'm not discussing this with you.

860
00:37:16,867 --> 00:37:18,317
Jiang Xiaotong is my daughter.

861
00:37:19,226 --> 00:37:21,876
It's my right to teach her in my way.

862
00:37:21,987 --> 00:37:24,516
You have no say in this matter.

863
00:37:24,547 --> 00:37:26,077
I hope you won't make

864
00:37:26,306 --> 00:37:28,197
such a stupid mistake again.

865
00:37:28,306 --> 00:37:30,237
She's only a teenager.

866
00:37:30,306 --> 00:37:32,466
She can choose what she wants to do

867
00:37:32,467 --> 00:37:34,066
and who she wants to be.

868
00:37:34,067 --> 00:37:35,506
Why do you have to

869
00:37:35,507 --> 00:37:36,386
keep forcing everyone

870
00:37:36,387 --> 00:37:38,157
to become who you want us to be?

871
00:37:39,586 --> 00:37:40,597
What are you getting at?

872
00:37:45,746 --> 00:37:48,197
Jiang Xiaotong, Jiang Jiaqiao, and me.

873
00:37:48,947 --> 00:37:50,757
Have you ever respected us?

874
00:37:51,706 --> 00:37:52,466
Have you ever asked us

875
00:37:52,467 --> 00:37:53,717
about what we truly wanted?

876
00:37:54,666 --> 00:37:56,265
Do you think this is the way
to show us care?

877
00:37:56,266 --> 00:37:57,906
I'm telling you, no!

878
00:37:57,907 --> 00:38:00,625
You are stripping us of our basic rights.

879
00:38:00,626 --> 00:38:01,506
Let me tell you this.

880
00:38:01,507 --> 00:38:02,876
You do not have the right to do that.

881
00:38:03,387 --> 00:38:04,996
Yes, I do.

882
00:38:05,027 --> 00:38:06,036
No, you don't.

883
00:38:06,467 --> 00:38:07,356
Stand right there.

884
00:38:07,827 --> 00:38:09,677
Are you insane?

885
00:38:09,706 --> 00:38:11,346
Let's make this clear.

886
00:38:11,347 --> 00:38:12,145
What are you doing?

887
00:38:12,146 --> 00:38:13,197
Let go of me!

888
00:38:22,467 --> 00:38:23,876
Stop challenging me ever again.

889
00:38:37,507 --> 00:38:40,717
Mom, is Dad a bad guy?

890
00:38:41,146 --> 00:38:42,996
Why are you asking this?

891
00:38:43,027 --> 00:38:45,105
Dad didn't pick up our calls.

892
00:38:45,106 --> 00:38:47,836
Does Dad not want us anymore?

893
00:38:47,907 --> 00:38:50,745
Dou's dad didn't answer his call,

894
00:38:50,746 --> 00:38:53,757
and his mom thought he was a bad guy.

895
00:38:54,387 --> 00:38:56,717
You miss Dad, don't you?

896
00:38:58,266 --> 00:38:59,916
We miss you too, Mom.

897
00:39:01,427 --> 00:39:03,637
I'll be back soon to fetch you.

898
00:39:03,827 --> 00:39:06,105
In the meantime,

899
00:39:06,106 --> 00:39:10,197
do listen to Grandpa and Grandma, okay?

900
00:39:10,507 --> 00:39:12,597
Okay, Mom.

901
00:39:13,347 --> 00:39:14,346
Bye-bye.

902
00:39:14,347 --> 00:39:15,546
I'll come and fetch you back soon.

903
00:39:15,547 --> 00:39:17,036
Bye-bye.

904
00:39:17,306 --> 00:39:18,237
Bye-bye.

905
00:39:30,786 --> 00:39:32,916
Attorney Wu, could you please

906
00:39:33,186 --> 00:39:33,906
look into

907
00:39:33,907 --> 00:39:35,916
Gao Ping's situation now?

908
00:39:45,427 --> 00:39:47,197
(Attorney Wu: Gao Ping has been transferred
to the detention center.)

909
00:39:47,507 --> 00:39:48,346
(I heard that his aunt)

910
00:39:48,347 --> 00:39:49,305
(is selling her house)

911
00:39:49,306 --> 00:39:50,436
(to raise money for him.)

912
00:40:10,907 --> 00:40:12,237
Why are you up?

913
00:40:13,467 --> 00:40:13,906
Come.

914
00:40:13,907 --> 00:40:15,396
I saw you got up.

915
00:40:18,106 --> 00:40:19,476
Do you really believe

916
00:40:19,507 --> 00:40:21,077
Haiyang and Xiang Zhong

917
00:40:21,507 --> 00:40:23,757
ran into each other there earlier today?

918
00:40:26,947 --> 00:40:28,956
Do you believe in
the coincidence like that?

919
00:40:31,226 --> 00:40:32,105
So

920
00:40:32,106 --> 00:40:34,036
they might get back together?

921
00:40:35,949 --> 00:40:38,077
It'll be good

922
00:40:38,306 --> 00:40:39,516
if that's true.

923
00:40:40,146 --> 00:40:42,117
But Haiyang's mom

924
00:40:42,867 --> 00:40:44,237
is such a pain.

925
00:40:46,387 --> 00:40:48,916
Still, they can't abandon her.

926
00:40:53,586 --> 00:40:54,597
You see,

927
00:40:54,827 --> 00:40:56,876
what's wrong with these two girls?

928
00:40:57,467 --> 00:40:58,556
Xiang Nan

929
00:40:59,226 --> 00:41:00,466
married Jiang Hongbin,

930
00:41:00,467 --> 00:41:02,117
who has a troublesome sister.

931
00:41:02,427 --> 00:41:03,145
Xiang Zhong

932
00:41:03,146 --> 00:41:05,237
married Haiyang, who is pretty good,

933
00:41:06,306 --> 00:41:07,876
but his mom is a problem.

934
00:41:08,427 --> 00:41:10,077
As for me,

935
00:41:10,106 --> 00:41:12,117
I have the little tag-along.

936
00:41:13,186 --> 00:41:15,117
Did they take it after us?

937
00:41:15,626 --> 00:41:16,745
Is it after me

938
00:41:16,746 --> 00:41:17,876
or after you?

939
00:41:19,266 --> 00:41:20,785
You're so blessed.

940
00:41:20,786 --> 00:41:22,356
You're different from their case.

941
00:41:22,427 --> 00:41:23,597
Certainly.

942
00:41:24,186 --> 00:41:25,757
These two girls

943
00:41:26,146 --> 00:41:27,317
didn't inherit good fortune

944
00:41:27,347 --> 00:41:28,836
from us.

945
00:41:29,867 --> 00:41:31,677
They're not as lucky as I am.

946
00:42:15,027 --> 00:42:16,556
Why didn't you come home last night?

947
00:42:20,746 --> 00:42:22,556
I was working at my studio.

948
00:42:33,427 --> 00:42:34,745
There are

949
00:42:34,746 --> 00:42:36,356
twelve golden toads in total.

950
00:42:36,947 --> 00:42:39,597
I wish you and your friends great success.

951
00:42:47,106 --> 00:42:48,996
I was too impulsive yesterday.

952
00:42:49,106 --> 00:42:50,117
I'm sorry.

953
00:42:51,347 --> 00:42:52,597
How about this, Xiang Nan?

954
00:42:53,067 --> 00:42:54,757
I'll cancel all my appointments
this afternoon.

955
00:42:55,067 --> 00:42:56,036
Let's go shopping.

956
00:42:56,106 --> 00:42:57,197
As long as you're happy,

957
00:42:57,226 --> 00:42:59,797
I'll buy anything you like.

958
00:43:01,226 --> 00:43:02,637
I want a divorce.

959
00:43:23,014 --> 00:43:25,690
Something will eventually be lost

960
00:43:26,549 --> 00:43:29,072
Never to be remembered

961
00:43:30,243 --> 00:43:33,290
The intermittent news drifting away

962
00:43:33,727 --> 00:43:36,440
And then forgotten

963
00:43:37,174 --> 00:43:40,498
Who can still face life?

964
00:43:40,905 --> 00:43:43,458
With the courage it gives

965
00:43:44,141 --> 00:43:45,443
Whether looking down

966
00:43:45,916 --> 00:43:47,440
Or holding heads high

967
00:43:48,054 --> 00:43:50,854
We must stay together

968
00:43:51,501 --> 00:43:54,919
Walking through the cool night breeze

969
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:57,930
Leaving not a trace of sadness

970
